/* Sibling imports */

/* Override Blueprint's _reset.scss styles */
html {
  box-sizing: unset;
}

*,
*::before,
*::after {
  box-sizing: unset;
}

body {
  color: unset;
  font-family: var(--jp-ui-font-family);
}

p {
  margin-top: unset;
  margin-bottom: unset;
}

small {
  font-size: unset;
}

strong {
  font-weight: unset;
}

/* Override Blueprint's _typography.scss styles */
a {
  text-decoration: unset;
  color: unset;
}
a:hover {
  text-decoration: unset;
  color: unset;
}

/* Override Blueprint's _accessibility.scss styles */
:focus {
  outline: unset;
  outline-offset: unset;
  -moz-outline-radius: unset;
}

/* Styles for ui-components */
.jp-Button {
  border-radius: var(--jp-border-radius);
  padding: 0px 12px;
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size1);
}

/* Use our own theme for hover styles */
button.jp-Button.bp3-button.bp3-minimal:hover {
  background-color: var(--jp-layout-color2);
}
.jp-Button.minimal {
  color: unset !important;
}

.jp-Button.jp-ToolbarButtonComponent {
  text-transform: none;
}

.jp-InputGroup input {
  box-sizing: border-box;
  border-radius: 0;
  background-color: transparent;
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color0);
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 var(--jp-border-width) var(--jp-input-border-color);
}

.jp-InputGroup input:focus {
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 var(--jp-border-width)
      var(--jp-input-active-box-shadow-color),
    inset 0 0 0 3px var(--jp-input-active-box-shadow-color);
}

.jp-InputGroup input::placeholder,
input::placeholder {
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color3);
}

.jp-BPIcon {
  display: inline-block;
  vertical-align: middle;
  margin: auto;
}

/* Stop blueprint futzing with our icon fills */
.bp3-icon.jp-BPIcon > svg:not([fill]) {
  fill: var(--jp-inverse-layout-color3);
}

.jp-InputGroupAction {
  padding: 6px;
}

.jp-HTMLSelect.jp-DefaultStyle select {
  background-color: initial;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 0;
  box-shadow: none;
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color0);
  display: block;
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size1);
  height: 24px;
  line-height: 14px;
  padding: 0 25px 0 10px;
  text-align: left;
  -moz-appearance: none;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
}

/* Use our own theme for hover and option styles */
.jp-HTMLSelect.jp-DefaultStyle select:hover,
.jp-HTMLSelect.jp-DefaultStyle select > option {
  background-color: var(--jp-layout-color2);
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color0);
}
select {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

/*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Search
|----------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

.lm-CommandPalette-search {
  padding: 4px;
  background-color: var(--jp-layout-color1);
  z-index: 2;
}

.lm-CommandPalette-wrapper {
  overflow: overlay;
  padding: 0px 9px;
  background-color: var(--jp-input-active-background);
  height: 30px;
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 var(--jp-border-width) var(--jp-input-border-color);
}

.lm-CommandPalette.lm-mod-focused .lm-CommandPalette-wrapper {
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px var(--jp-input-active-box-shadow-color),
    inset 0 0 0 3px var(--jp-input-active-box-shadow-color);
}

.lm-CommandPalette-wrapper::after {
  content: ' ';
  color: white;
  background-color: var(--jp-brand-color1);
  position: absolute;
  top: 4px;
  right: 4px;
  height: 30px;
  width: 10px;
  padding: 0px 10px;
  background-image: var(--jp-icon-search-white);
  background-size: 20px;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: center;
}

.lm-CommandPalette-input {
  background: transparent;
  width: calc(100% - 18px);
  float: left;
  border: none;
  outline: none;
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size1);
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color0);
  line-height: var(--jp-private-commandpalette-search-height);
}

.lm-CommandPalette-input::-webkit-input-placeholder,
.lm-CommandPalette-input::-moz-placeholder,
.lm-CommandPalette-input:-ms-input-placeholder {
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color3);
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size1);
}

/*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Results
|----------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

.lm-CommandPalette-header:first-child {
  margin-top: 0px;
}

.lm-CommandPalette-header {
  border-bottom: solid var(--jp-border-width) var(--jp-border-color2);
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color1);
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex;
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size0);
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  margin-top: 8px;
  padding: 8px 0 8px 12px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.lm-CommandPalette-header.lm-mod-active {
  background: var(--jp-layout-color2);
}

.lm-CommandPalette-header > mark {
  background-color: transparent;
  font-weight: bold;
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color1);
}

.lm-CommandPalette-item {
  padding: 4px 12px 4px 4px;
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color1);
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size1);
  font-weight: 400;
  display: flex;
}

.lm-CommandPalette-item.lm-mod-disabled {
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color3);
}

.lm-CommandPalette-item.lm-mod-active {
  background: var(--jp-layout-color3);
}

.lm-CommandPalette-item.lm-mod-active:hover:not(.lm-mod-disabled) {
  background: var(--jp-layout-color4);
}

.lm-CommandPalette-item:hover:not(.lm-mod-active):not(.lm-mod-disabled) {
  background: var(--jp-layout-color2);
}

.lm-CommandPalette-itemContent {
  overflow: hidden;
}

.lm-CommandPalette-itemLabel > mark {
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color0);
  background-color: transparent;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.lm-CommandPalette-item.lm-mod-disabled mark {
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color3);
}

.lm-CommandPalette-item .lm-CommandPalette-itemIcon {
  margin: 0 4px 0 0;
  position: relative;
  width: 16px;
  top: 2px;
  flex: 0 0 auto;
}

.lm-CommandPalette-item.lm-mod-disabled .lm-CommandPalette-itemIcon {
  opacity: 0.4;
}

.lm-CommandPalette-item .lm-CommandPalette-itemShortcut {
  flex: 0 0 auto;
}

.lm-CommandPalette-itemCaption {
  display: none;
}

.lm-CommandPalette-content {
  background-color: var(--jp-layout-color1);
}

.lm-CommandPalette-content:empty:after {
  content: 'No results';
  margin: auto;
  margin-top: 20px;
  width: 100px;
  display: block;
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size2);
  font-family: var(--jp-ui-font-family);
  font-weight: lighter;
}

.lm-CommandPalette-emptyMessage {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 24px;
  line-height: 1.32;
  padding: 0px 8px;
  color: var(--jp-content-font-color3);
}

.jp-Dialog {
  position: absolute;
  z-index: 10000;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  top: 0px;
  left: 0px;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--jp-dialog-background);
}

.jp-Dialog-content {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  background: var(--jp-layout-color1);
  padding: 24px;
  padding-bottom: 12px;
  min-width: 300px;
  min-height: 150px;
  max-width: 1000px;
  max-height: 500px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  box-shadow: var(--jp-elevation-z20);
  word-wrap: break-word;
  border-radius: var(--jp-border-radius);
  /* This is needed so that all font sizing of children done in ems is
   * relative to this base size */
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size1);
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color1);
}

.jp-Dialog-button {
  overflow: visible;
}

button.jp-Dialog-button:focus {
  outline: 1px solid var(--jp-brand-color1);
  outline-offset: 4px;
  -moz-outline-radius: 0px;
}

button.jp-Dialog-button:focus::-moz-focus-inner {
  border: 0;
}

.jp-Dialog-header {
  flex: 0 0 auto;
  padding-bottom: 12px;
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size3);
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color0);
}

.jp-Dialog-body {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  flex: 1 1 auto;
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size1);
  background: var(--jp-layout-color1);
  overflow: auto;
}

.jp-Dialog-footer {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: row;
  justify-content: flex-end;
  flex: 0 0 auto;
  margin-left: -12px;
  margin-right: -12px;
  padding: 12px;
}

.jp-Dialog-title {
  overflow: hidden;
  white-space: nowrap;
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
}

.jp-Dialog-body > .jp-select-wrapper {
  width: 100%;
}

.jp-Dialog-body > button {
  padding: 0px 16px;
}

.jp-Dialog-body > label {
  line-height: 1.4;
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color0);
}

.jp-Dialog-button.jp-mod-styled:not(:last-child) {
  margin-right: 12px;
}

/*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Copyright (c) 2014-2016, Jupyter Development Team.
|
| Distributed under the terms of the Modified BSD License.
|----------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

.jp-HoverBox {
  position: fixed;
}

.jp-HoverBox.jp-mod-outofview {
  display: none;
}

/*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Copyright (c) Jupyter Development Team.
| Distributed under the terms of the Modified BSD License.
|----------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

.jp-IFrame {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}

.jp-IFrame > iframe {
  border: none;
}

/*
When drag events occur, `p-mod-override-cursor` is added to the body.
Because iframes steal all cursor events, the following two rules are necessary
to suppress pointer events while resize drags are occurring. There may be a
better solution to this problem.
*/
body.lm-mod-override-cursor .jp-IFrame {
  position: relative;
}

body.lm-mod-override-cursor .jp-IFrame:before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  background: transparent;
}

/*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Copyright (c) 2014-2016, Jupyter Development Team.
|
| Distributed under the terms of the Modified BSD License.
|----------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

.jp-MainAreaWidget > :focus {
  outline: none;
}

.jp-Spinner {
  position: absolute;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  z-index: 10;
  left: 0;
  top: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--jp-layout-color0);
  outline: none;
}

.jp-SpinnerContent {
  font-size: 10px;
  margin: 50px auto;
  text-indent: -9999em;
  width: 3em;
  height: 3em;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--jp-brand-color3);
  background: linear-gradient(
    to right,
    #f37626 10%,
    rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 42%
  );
  position: relative;
  animation: load3 1s infinite linear, fadeIn 1s;
}

.jp-SpinnerContent:before {
  width: 50%;
  height: 50%;
  background: #f37626;
  border-radius: 100% 0 0 0;
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  content: '';
}

.jp-SpinnerContent:after {
  background: var(--jp-layout-color0);
  width: 75%;
  height: 75%;
  border-radius: 50%;
  content: '';
  margin: auto;
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  right: 0;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  0% {
    opacity: 0;
  }
  100% {
    opacity: 1;
  }
}

@keyframes load3 {
  0% {
    transform: rotate(0deg);
  }
  100% {
    transform: rotate(360deg);
  }
}

button.jp-mod-styled {
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size1);
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color0);
  border: none;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  padding: 0px 12px;
  letter-spacing: 0.8px;
  outline: none;
  appearance: none;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  -moz-appearance: none;
}

input.jp-mod-styled {
  background: var(--jp-input-background);
  height: 28px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  border: var(--jp-border-width) solid var(--jp-border-color1);
  padding-left: 7px;
  padding-right: 7px;
  font-size: var(--jp-ui-font-size2);
  color: var(--jp-ui-font-color0);
  outline: none;
  appearance: none;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  -moz-appearance: none;
}

input.jp-mod-styled:focus {

button.jp-ToolbarButtonComponent span {

.jp-Notebook .jp-Cell {
  overflow: visible;
}

.jp-Notebook .jp-Cell .jp-InputPrompt {
  cursor: move;
}

/*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Notebook state related styling
|
| The notebook and cells each have states, here are the possibilities:
|
| - Notebook
|   - Command
|   - Edit
| - Cell
|   - None
|   - Active (only one can be active)
|   - Selected (the cells actions are applied to)

|----------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

/* Command or edit modes */

.jp-Notebook .jp-Cell:not(.jp-mod-active) .jp-InputPrompt {
  opacity: var(--jp-cell-prompt-not-active-opacity);
  color: var(--jp-cell-prompt-not-active-font-color);

.jp-Notebook.jp-mod-commandMode .jp-Cell.jp-mod-selected {
  background: var(--jp-notebook-multiselected-color);

  background: transparent;

.jp-Notebook.jp-mod-editMode .jp-Cell.jp-mod-active .jp-InputArea-editor {
  border: var(--jp-border-width) solid var(--jp-cell-editor-active-border-color);

}

.jp-dragImage-multipleBack {
  z-index: -1;

  width: 300px;
  top: 8px;
  left: 8px;
  background: var(--jp-layout-color2);
  border: var(--jp-border-width) solid var(--jp-input-border-color);
  box-shadow: 2px 2px 4px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);

/*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

.jp-NotebookTools {

.jp-RankedPanel > :not(:first-child) {

<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1">##Inicializacija metod </span>

<span class="c1">##################################################</span>
<span class="c1">## Buy stocks if you have money simulation [WITH PROVISION]</span>
<span class="c1">###################################################</span>
<span class="c1">#pridobi celoten denar, ki ti pripada </span>
<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">getAllMoneyFromStoks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="c1">#prodaj vse delnice</span>
    <span class="c1">#Get money from stocks</span>
    <span class="n">counter</span>  <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>
    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">x</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])):</span>
        <span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">):</span>
            <span class="n">tmp_money</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">money</span>
            <span class="n">money_from_sell</span>  <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>
            <span class="n">profit</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">money_from_sell</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
              <span class="c1">#---------OBDAVITEV DOBIKA 30% ---------------</span>
            <span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">profit</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">):</span>
                <span class="n">profit</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">profit</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="mf">0.7</span>
            <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">profit</span>    
            <span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">=</span><span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">profit</span> <span class="c1">#cena * tevilo</span>
            
            <span class="n">ind</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">ind</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">#zap_id</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;SELL&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#akcija</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_money</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#zacetni kapital</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#simbol</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#buy on / sell on [date]</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#cena</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#kolicina</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#koncni kapital</span>
            
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
        <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span> 
            <span class="n">counter</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">counter</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mi">1</span> 
    <span class="c1">#prodaj vse dividende</span>
    <span class="n">counter</span>  <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>
    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">x</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])):</span>
        <span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">):</span>
            <span class="n">tmp_money</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">money</span>
            <span class="c1">#---------OBDAVITEV DIVIDENDE 30% ---------------</span>
            <span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">=</span><span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mf">0.7</span>
            <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mf">0.7</span>
            <span class="n">ind</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">ind</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">#zap_id</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;GET&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#akcija</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_money</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#zacetni kapital</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#simbol</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#buy on / sell on [date]</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#cena</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#kolicina</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">)</span>  

            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
        <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span> 
            <span class="c1">#print(bought_dividents[0][counter], &quot;&lt;&quot;,tmp_day )</span>
            <span class="n">counter</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">counter</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span>
  
<span class="c1">#---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------    </span>
<span class="c1">##### Kupi delnico</span>
<span class="c1">#---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------    </span>
<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">buyStocks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">index_path</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="c1">#Dodaj indek na index_path</span>
    <span class="n">index_path</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">)</span>
    
    <span class="c1">#odstej denar</span>
    <span class="n">tmp_money</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">money</span>
    <span class="n">num_of_bought_stocks</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">])</span>
    <span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">num_of_bought_stocks</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">])</span>
    
    <span class="c1">#zapii v info list</span>
    <span class="n">ind</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span>
    <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">ind</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">#zap_id</span>
    <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;BUY&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#akcija</span>
    <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_money</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#zacetni kapital</span>
    <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#simbol</span>
    <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#buy on / sell on [date]</span>
    <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#cena</span>
    <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">num_of_bought_stocks</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#kolicina</span>
    <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#koncni kapital</span>
    
    <span class="c1">#print(&quot;BUY: Zac_kap:&quot;,tmp_money,&quot;|sym:&quot;,rek_data[6][tmp_index],&quot;|buy on:&quot;,rek_data[0][tmp_index],&quot;|price:&quot;,rek_data[3][tmp_index],&quot;|Num:&quot;,num_of_bought_stocks,&quot;|money:&quot;,money) </span>
    
    <span class="c1">#DOdaj delnico na bought_stocks</span>
    <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="c1">#ex_date</span>
    <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="c1">#price_on_ex_day_open</span>
    <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">num_of_bought_stocks</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">#number_of_dividents_bought</span>
    <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="c1">#simbol</span>
    <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_money</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">#------------------&gt; Cena nakupa</span>
    
    <span class="c1">#DOdaj dividendo na bought_dividents</span>
    <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="c1">#pay_d</span>
    <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="c1">#dividents_price</span>
    <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">num_of_bought_stocks</span><span class="p">)</span>   <span class="c1">#number_of_dividents_bought</span>
    <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="c1">#simbol</span>
    
    
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">index_path</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span>

<span class="c1">#---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------    </span>
<span class="c1">#Pridobi denar od prodaje delnic  </span>
<span class="c1">#---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------    </span>
<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">getMoneyFromStoks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="c1">#Get money from stocks</span>
    <span class="n">counter</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">x</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])):</span>
        <span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">):</span>
            <span class="n">tmp_money</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">money</span>
            <span class="n">money_from_sell</span>  <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>
            <span class="n">profit</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">money_from_sell</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="c1">#---------OBDAVITEV DOBIKA 30% ---------------</span>
            <span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">profit</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">):</span>
                <span class="n">profit</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">profit</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="mf">0.7</span>
            <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">profit</span>
           <span class="c1"># print( bought_stocks[4][counter], profit)</span>
            <span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">=</span><span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">profit</span> <span class="c1">#cena * tevilo</span>
            <span class="c1">#zapii v info list</span>
            <span class="n">ind</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">ind</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">#zap_id</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;SELL&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#akcija</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_money</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#zacetni kapital</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#simbol</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#buy on / sell on [date]</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#cena</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#kolicina</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#koncni kapital</span>
            
            <span class="c1">#print(&quot;SELL Zac_kap: &quot;,tmp_money,&quot;|sym:&quot;,bought_stocks[3][counter],&quot;|sell date:&quot;,bought_stocks[0][counter],&quot;|amount:&quot;,bought_stocks[2][counter],&quot;|Money:&quot;,money)</span>
            <span class="c1">#izbrisi iz seznama</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
        <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">counter</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">counter</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
    
    <span class="c1">#Get money from divident</span>
    <span class="n">counter</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">x</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])):</span>
        <span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">):</span>
            <span class="n">tmp_money</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">money</span>
             <span class="c1">#---------OBDAVITEV DIVIDENDE 30% ---------------</span>
            <span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">=</span><span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="mf">0.7</span> <span class="c1">#cena * tevilo</span>
            <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="mf">0.7</span> 
            <span class="c1">#zapii v info list</span>
            <span class="n">ind</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">ind</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1">#zap_id</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;GET&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#akcija</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_money</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#zacetni kapital</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#simbol</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#buy on / sell on [date]</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#cena</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">])</span>    <span class="c1">#kolicina</span>
            <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1">#koncni kapital</span>
            <span class="c1">#print(&quot;GET  Zac_kap: &quot;,tmp_money,&quot;sym:&quot;,bought_dividents[3][counter],&quot;sell date: &quot;,bought_dividents[0][counter],&quot;amount:&quot;,bought_dividents[2][counter], &quot;Money:&quot;,money)</span>
           
            <span class="c1">#izbrisi iz seznama</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
            <span class="k">del</span> <span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">counter</span><span class="p">]</span>
        <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">counter</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">counter</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mi">1</span>              
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span>

<span class="n">bought_dividents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[[],[],[],[]]</span>
<span class="n">tmp_day</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>

<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">x</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])):</span>
    <span class="c1">#Pridobi denar, ki ti pripada</span>
    <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_list_bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_list_bought_dividents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">getMoneyFromStoks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="c1">#v primeru, da lahko kupi ,kupi</span>
    <span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">]):</span>
        <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">index_path</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">buyStocks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">index_path</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">)</span>


<span class="n">df</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span><span class="p">({</span><span class="s2">&quot;zap_id&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;akcija&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;zac_kap&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span>
                  <span class="s2">&quot;sim&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;date&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;cena&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;kol&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;kon_kap&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">],</span>
                  <span class="p">})</span>

<span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">):</span>    
    <span class="n">tmp_day</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>    
<span class="k">while</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">!=</span> <span class="mi">0</span> <span class="ow">or</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">!=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">getAllMoneyFromStoks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">df</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span><span class="p">({</span><span class="s2">&quot;zap_id&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="c1">#Zaporedna tevilka</span>

                   <span class="s2">&quot;kol&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">],</span>    <span class="c1">#koliina delnice/dividende</span>

     <div class="CodeMirror cm-s-jupyter">
<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1">#podatki za leto 2013-2014</span>
<span class="n">year</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;2013&quot;</span>
<span class="n">mycursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;SELECT s.simbol,s.dec_d,s.ex_d,s.pay_d,s.stock_price_before_ex_date,s.stock_price_on_dec_date,s.price_on_ex_day_open,s.dividend,s.proc_dec_buy FROM bxhrkfcck4ktii1ojqu2.stock s,(SELECT simbol, AVG(proc_dec_buy) AS povprecje FROM bxhrkfcck4ktii1ojqu2.stock WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM dec_d) &lt; &quot;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">year</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s2">&quot; GROUP BY simbol) m WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.dec_d) &gt;= &quot;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">year</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s2">&quot; AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.dec_d) &lt;= &quot;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">year</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s2">&quot; AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.pay_d) &lt;= &quot;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">year</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s2">&quot; AND s.simbol = m.simbol AND m.povprecje &gt; &quot;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">povprecje1</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s2">&quot; AND m.povprecje &lt; &quot;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">povprecje2</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s2">&quot; ORDER BY dec_d,ex_d,pay_d DESC&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="c1">#SELECT s.simbol,</span>
<span class="c1">#SELECT s.simbol,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.dec_d,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.ex_d,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.pay_d,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.stock_price_before_ex_date,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.stock_price_on_dec_date,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.price_on_ex_day_open,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.dividend,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.proc_dec_buy</span>
<span class="c1">#FROM bxhrkfcck4ktii1ojqu2.stock s,</span>
<span class="c1">#     (SELECT simbol,</span>
<span class="c1">#            AVG(proc_dec_buy) AS povprecje </span>
<span class="c1">#      FROM bxhrkfcck4ktii1ojqu2.stock</span>
<span class="c1">#      WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM dec_d) &lt; year</span>
<span class="c1">#      GROUP BY simbol) m </span>
<span class="c1">#WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.dec_d) &gt;= year </span>
<span class="c1">#  AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.dec_d) &lt;= year</span>
<span class="c1">#  AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.pay_d) &lt;= year</span>
<span class="c1">#  AND s.simbol = m.simbol </span>
<span class="c1">#  AND m.povprecje &gt; povprecje1</span>
<span class="c1">#  AND m.povprecje &gt; povprecje2</span>
<span class="c1">#ORDERBY dec_d, ex_d, pay_d DESC</span>


<span class="n">myresult</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">mycursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fetchall</span><span class="p">()</span>

<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1">###################################################</span>
<span class="c1">#Kupovanje delnic ko ima denar za leto 2013-2014</span>
<span class="c1">###################################################</span>
<span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="c1">#zadnja vrednost iz prejsnega leta</span>
<span class="n">info_list</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[[],[],[],[],[],[],[],[]]</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;##################################################&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;VHODNI PODATKI ZA LETO 2013-2014&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;##################################################&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;Zaetni kapital:&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">money</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;Davek na dobiek pri prodaji finannega intrumenta: 30%&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;Davek na dividendo: 30%&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">index_path</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
<span class="n">bought_stocks</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[[],[],[],[],[]]</span> <span class="c1">#---&gt;dodamo e ceno nakupa</span>
<span class="n">bought_dividents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[[],[],[],[]]</span>
<span class="n">tmp_day</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">tmp_kapital</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">money</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">x</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])):</span>
    <span class="c1">#Pridobi denar, ki ti pripada</span>
    <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_list_bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_list_bought_dividents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">getMoneyFromStoks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="c1">#v primeru, da lahko kupi ,kupi</span>
    <span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">]):</span>
        <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">index_path</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">buyStocks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">index_path</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">)</span>


<span class="n">df</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span><span class="p">({</span><span class="s2">&quot;zap_id&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;akcija&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;zac_kap&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span>
                  <span class="s2">&quot;sim&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;date&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;cena&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;kol&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;kon_kap&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">],</span>
                  <span class="p">})</span>

<span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">):</span>    
    <span class="n">tmp_day</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>    
<span class="k">while</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">!=</span> <span class="mi">0</span> <span class="ow">or</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">!=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">getAllMoneyFromStoks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">tmp_day</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tmp_day</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">timedelta</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">days</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">df</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span><span class="p">({</span><span class="s2">&quot;zap_id&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="c1">#Zaporedna tevilka</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;akcija&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="c1">#Akcija</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;zac_kap&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="c1">#Zacetni kapital</span>
                  <span class="s2">&quot;sim&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span>     <span class="c1">#Simbol</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;date&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>   <span class="c1">#Datum izvedene akcije</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;cena&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">],</span>   <span class="c1">#cena delnice/dividende</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;kol&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">],</span>    <span class="c1">#koliina delnice/dividende</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;kon_kap&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="c1">#kapital ob koncu akcije</span>
                  <span class="p">})</span>

<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;-------------------------------------------------------------&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>

<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1">#podatki za leto 2013-2014</span>

<span class="c1">#SELECT s.simbol,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.dec_d,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.ex_d,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.pay_d,</span>

<span class="c1">#       s.dividend,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.proc_dec_buy</span>
<span class="c1">#FROM bxhrkfcck4ktii1ojqu2.stock s,</span>
<span class="c1">#     (SELECT simbol,</span>
<span class="c1">#            AVG(proc_dec_buy) AS povprecje </span>
<span class="c1">#      FROM bxhrkfcck4ktii1ojqu2.stock</span>
<span class="c1">#      WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM dec_d) &lt; year</span>
<span class="c1">#      GROUP BY simbol) m </span>
<span class="c1">#WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.dec_d) &gt;= year </span>
<span class="c1">#  AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.dec_d) &lt;= year</span>
<span class="c1">#  AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.pay_d) &lt;= year</span>
<span class="c1">#  AND s.simbol = m.simbol </span>
<span class="c1">#  AND m.povprecje &gt; povprecje1</span>
<span class="c1">#  AND m.povprecje &gt; povprecje2</span>
<span class="c1">#ORDERBY dec_d, ex_d, pay_d DESC</span>

    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">)</span>

     <div class="CodeMirror cm-s-jupyter">
<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1">#podatki za leto 2015-2016</span>
<span class="n">year</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;2015&quot;</span>
<span class="n">mycursor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">execute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;SELECT s.simbol,s.dec_d,s.ex_d,s.pay_d,s.stock_price_before_ex_date,s.stock_price_on_dec_date,s.price_on_ex_day_open,s.dividend,s.proc_dec_buy FROM bxhrkfcck4ktii1ojqu2.stock s,(SELECT simbol, AVG(proc_dec_buy) AS povprecje FROM bxhrkfcck4ktii1ojqu2.stock WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM dec_d) &lt; &quot;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">year</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s2">&quot; GROUP BY simbol) m WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.dec_d) &gt;= &quot;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">year</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s2">&quot; AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.dec_d) &lt;= &quot;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">year</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s2">&quot; AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.pay_d) &lt;= &quot;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">year</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s2">&quot; AND s.simbol = m.simbol AND m.povprecje &gt; &quot;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">povprecje1</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s2">&quot; AND m.povprecje &lt; &quot;</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">povprecje2</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="s2">&quot; ORDER BY dec_d,ex_d,pay_d DESC&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="c1">#SELECT s.simbol,</span>
<span class="c1">#SELECT s.simbol,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.dec_d,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.ex_d,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.pay_d,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.stock_price_before_ex_date,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.stock_price_on_dec_date,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.price_on_ex_day_open,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.dividend,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.proc_dec_buy</span>
<span class="c1">#FROM bxhrkfcck4ktii1ojqu2.stock s,</span>
<span class="c1">#     (SELECT simbol,</span>
<span class="c1">#            AVG(proc_dec_buy) AS povprecje </span>
<span class="c1">#      FROM bxhrkfcck4ktii1ojqu2.stock</span>
<span class="c1">#      WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM dec_d) &lt; year</span>
<span class="c1">#      GROUP BY simbol) m </span>
