    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="c1">#v primeru, da lahko kupi ,kupi</span>
    <span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">]):</span>
        <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">index_path</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">buyStocks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">index_path</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">)</span>


<span class="n">df</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span><span class="p">({</span><span class="s2">&quot;zap_id&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;akcija&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;zac_kap&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span>
                  <span class="s2">&quot;sim&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;date&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;cena&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;kol&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;kon_kap&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">],</span>
                  <span class="p">})</span>

<span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">):</span>    
    <span class="n">tmp_day</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>    
<span class="k">while</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">!=</span> <span class="mi">0</span> <span class="ow">or</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">!=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">getAllMoneyFromStoks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">df</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span><span class="p">({</span><span class="s2">&quot;zap_id&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="c1">#Zaporedna tevilka</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;akcija&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="c1">#Akcija</span>

                  <span class="s2">&quot;sim&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span>     <span class="c1">#Simbol</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;date&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>   <span class="c1">#Datum izvedene akcije</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;cena&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">],</span>   <span class="c1">#cena delnice/dividende</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;kol&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">],</span>    <span class="c1">#koliina delnice/dividende</span>

                  <span class="p">})</span>

<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1">###################################################</span>
<span class="c1">#Kupovanje delnic ko ima denar za leto 2017-2018</span>
<span class="c1">###################################################</span>
<span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="c1">#zadnja vrednost iz prejsnega leta</span>
<span class="n">info_list</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[[],[],[],[],[],[],[],[]]</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;##################################################&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;VHODNI PODATKI ZA LETO 2017-2018&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;##################################################&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;Zaetni kapital:&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">money</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;Davek na dobiek pri prodaji finannega intrumenta: 30%&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;Davek na dividendo: 30%&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">index_path</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
<span class="n">bought_stocks</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[[],[],[],[],[]]</span> <span class="c1">#---&gt;dodamo e ceno nakupa</span>
<span class="n">bought_dividents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[[],[],[],[]]</span>
<span class="n">tmp_day</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">tmp_kapital</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">money</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">x</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])):</span>
    <span class="c1">#Pridobi denar, ki ti pripada</span>
    <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_list_bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_list_bought_dividents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">getMoneyFromStoks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="c1">#v primeru, da lahko kupi ,kupi</span>
    <span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">money</span> <span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">]):</span>
        <span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">index_path</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_index</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">buyStocks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">index_path</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">)</span>


<span class="n">df</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span><span class="p">({</span><span class="s2">&quot;zap_id&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;akcija&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;zac_kap&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">],</span>
                  <span class="s2">&quot;sim&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;date&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;cena&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;kol&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">],</span>
                   <span class="s2">&quot;kon_kap&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">],</span>
                  <span class="p">})</span>

<span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">):</span>    
    <span class="n">tmp_day</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>    
<span class="k">while</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">!=</span> <span class="mi">0</span> <span class="ow">or</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">!=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">getAllMoneyFromStoks</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">money</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_stocks</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">bought_dividents</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_day</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">date_and_price</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tmp_kapital</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">tmp_day</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tmp_day</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">timedelta</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">days</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">df</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span><span class="p">({</span><span class="s2">&quot;zap_id&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">info_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="c1">#Zaporedna tevilka</span>

<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1">#podatki za leto 2020-2021</span>

<span class="c1">#       s.dec_d,</span>
<span class="c1">#       s.ex_d,</span>

<span class="c1">#ORDERBY dec_d, ex_d, pay_d DESC</span>

    <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">rek_data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">])</span>
